'''Powerlevel9k''' is [[Article description::a theme for [[Zsh|ZSH]] which uses Powerline Fonts.]] It can be used with vanilla ZSH or ZSH frameworks such as Oh-My-Zsh, Prezto, Antigen, and many others.

== Installation ==

=== Prerequisites ===

The Powerlevel9k theme requires {{Package|app-shells/zsh}}.

== Configuration ==

After configuring zsh correctly, add this command at the begin of the {{Path|~/.zshrc}} file to source the Powerlevel9k theme:

{{FileBox|filename=~/.zshrc|lang=bash|1=
source "/usr/share/zsh-theme-powerlevel9k/powerlevel9k.zsh-theme"
}}

See git Powerlevel9k repository to configure more this theme: https://github.com/Powerlevel9k/powerlevel9k.

